{"tid":82771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【震驚七百萬人】葉劉不符合參選特首資格？","createTime":"2017-01-16T08:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T09:42:03.000Z","uid":56203,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ece2a3d5246b23924afa97eb803104369e75249a","tid":82771,"uid":56203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"大家都知道葉劉2003年下台後，去左美國讀書，呢樣野佢自己都成日攞黎講<br />\n<br />\n（葉劉淑儀）辭職後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>葉劉淑儀在2003年赴美國留學，2006年回港</strong></span>，並以政治人物身份加入政壇。（出處：維基百科[url]<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80#.E8.BE.AD.E5.AE.98.E4.B8.8B.E5.8F.B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580%23.E8.BE.AD.E5.AE.98.E4.B8.8B.E5.8F.B0&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=de23676b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80#.E8.BE.AD.E5.AE.98.E4.B8.8B.E5.8F.B0</a><br />\n[/url]）<br />\n<br />\n但請大家睇下《基本法》第44條：香港特別行政區行政長官由年滿四十周歲，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>在香港通常居住連續滿二十年</strong></span></span>並在外國無居留權的香港特別行政區永久性居民中的中國公民擔任。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">葉劉離開左香港兩三年<br />\n唔符合連續居港廿年　請選舉主任DQ佢！</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"c60d91032a450b2a6948fe43e65ea6c230f1fe12","tid":82771,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9b464d1aecce80a3b15966b5db901420433dc2","tid":82771,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"唔係咁計，除非佢呢三年一次都冇返過香港。再者去外國讀學點可能界定為移民性質的離港。"},{"pid":"04c8edbe9dd229a782a074cb6d906eb5ac755766","tid":82771,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"佢去美國之前有連續住20年就符合啦"},{"pid":"df0a856c14d283fef8d6d4b995ee2fa32ce4dc6c","tid":82771,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c64bf9ecf26d6e205c34077b279ecd32477f3f","tid":82771,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"就算唔得, 人大釋法通常居住二十年既定義咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a8267d363d2a52cc4a0b499166c4e696cbd4a0","tid":82771,"uid":56203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係咁計，除非佢呢三年一次都冇返過香港。再者去外國讀學點可能界定為移民性質的離港。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(頭盔) 所以我標題最尾有個&quot;？&quot;"},{"pid":"950e1710c99425d6b221fbdf1a94327dc54d963e","tid":82771,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"冇問題<br />\n釋法重新定義通常居住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81738e58d34f87e55fa8a2830e38227f51ea4ecf","tid":82771,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢去美國之前有連續住20年就符合啦</blockquote><br />\n基本法係由97開始計"},{"pid":"31a7b74fd378f667941791e98c9a774cb02938eb","tid":82771,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"算係俾個藉口孽瘤好落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776b9df58a5573d49b4f0975774cf63dff1ff624","tid":82771,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢去美國之前有連續住20年就符合啦</blockquote><br />\n基本法係由97開始計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁計法, 2017年之前都唔會有人符合條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687b090ac18106e892917f7ffeb21823d748d9b7","tid":82771,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢去美國之前有連續住20年就符合啦</blockquote><br />\n基本法係由97開始計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁計法, 2017年之前都唔會有人符合條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思即係, 用你個計法, 董曾梁三個都係非法特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e966c6e6c9f19d6b0d81ef8b351be6cb645450b2","tid":82771,"uid":71697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"震驚1,300,000,000人"},{"pid":"bf11fdadca59854f56df4ae9c706b3c609a87b6a","tid":82771,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇問題<br />\n釋法重新定義通常居住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗釋法<br />\n通常居港通常唔會計出國讀書個段時間<br />\n只要佢讀完之後喺返香港工作，或者定居就得<br />\n所以葉劉喺呢個層面上係冇問題"},{"pid":"701602115453fc80d043f483fe5c742d66c7999c","tid":82771,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"你要搞清楚咩叫「通常居住連續滿二十年」先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常居住好似有準測，以前讀econ學過唔記得左<br />\n有啲野係豁免左<br />\nbtw龍門都係任般架啦，立法會宣誓果陣建制咪又係有人讀唔準讀唔齊，一樣比佢pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9ae8d0ede6f905a0c7a190bd9b93ef4cd1bb04","tid":82771,"uid":1187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢去美國之前有連續住20年就符合啦</blockquote><br />\n基本法係由97開始計</blockquote><br />\n97 開始生效唔代表97 開始計喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6b6ca71c54914391818f8692cb5cd8ea7f4691","tid":82771,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"其實而家出左林鄭，佢都係陪跑使者啦應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報紙佬都當哂佢大茄"},{"pid":"48d762cd96178e5e8bd01ad3b5c1ae1e4ec2ebc6","tid":82771,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"你咁講林鄭係老董時代都去過英國讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cc342c16909095a705fdb2e4ad40c5283086b0","tid":82771,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇問題<br />\n釋法重新定義通常居住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾釋法玩曬,唉屌"},{"pid":"a0a327878048c63a98b680e07e900ea9bbc4e422","tid":82771,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"Quote from 選舉指引:<br />\n<br />\n通常在香港居住的人是指除偶爾暫時離開香港外，如出外渡假、<span style=\"color: red;\">離港出外留學</span>，該人慣常及一般為在港定居的目的在本港合法居住。每宗個案須按本身的資料審查。該人離港時間長短、離港理由、 他／她本 人、配偶、子女及父母居住的地點，以及 他／她 在香港所保持的聯繫等，都是相關的因素。"},{"pid":"4fdbd5e9d9a9bc785966991e52b3a8dbce23caf3","tid":82771,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Quote from 選舉指引:<br />\n<br />\n通常在香港居住的人是指除偶爾暫時離開香港外，如出外渡假、<span style=\"color: red;\">離港出外留學</span>，該人慣常及一般為在港定居的目的在本港合法居住。每宗個案須按本身的資料審查。該人離港時間長短、離港理由、 他／她本 人、配偶、子女及父母居住的地點，以及 他／她 在香港所保持的聯繫等，都是相關的因素。</blockquote><br />\n所以出去留學係冇問題照計通常居住既時期"},{"pid":"b4f56618bf4fe5af577c42753df4212bfc942a76","tid":82771,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"跟車太貼"},{"pid":"fc9bc1a5f66a32b5ff613323dd711899539a13ed","tid":82771,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}